Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain

Record Class Entity.Action

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp22.domain.Entity.Action
Record Components:
id - ID of the entity this action belongs to.
moveVector - Amount the entity moved by in this action.
oldDir - Direction entity was facing before action.
newDir - Direction entity is facing after action.
interaction - The interaction, if any that happened this action.
Enclosing class:
Entity<S extends Observable<S>>
public static record Entity.Action(int id, Maze.Point moveVector, Entity.Direction oldDir, Entity.Direction newDir, Entity.Action.Interaction interaction) extends Record
A record used to store an action taken. This will be used to revert actions when replaying a game.
